## Third-Party Code

### Search Light (GPL-3.0)

The `spotlight/` directory contains code ported from
[Search Light](https://github.com/icedman/search-light), which is licensed
under GPL-3.0. These files are dual-licensed under both GPL-3.0 (matching
the original) and MIT (for compatibility with MacTop):

- `spotlight/timer.js`
- `spotlight/style.js`
- `spotlight/effects/tint_effect.js`
- `spotlight/effects/*.glsl`

Files written specifically for MacTop (not derived from Search Light):
- `spotlight/spotlightOverlay.js`
- `spotlight/panelIndicator.js`
- `spotlight/keybinding.js`

The Search Light code has been substantially rewritten to integrate with
MacTop's architecture and lifecycle. Original attribution is preserved in
file headers.
